<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/781754-history-of-scientist">history of scientist?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_781754'><a id="like_count_community_question_781754" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/781754?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">1 like</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F1552518.Wonderful_Life">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/781754-history-of-scientist">5 years ago</a>
