          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780393307009" href="/book/show/36475.Wonderful_Life">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/223837-nicky?shelf=science-fact">science-fact</a>, 
