    <a title="Mario Krapp" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/101949941-mario-krapp"><img alt="Mario Krapp" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1578591666p2/101949941.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
